reviewText: The idea of a Toby Keith video collection is an excellent one but only 10 videos? There's room for at least double that and then some, and it's not as though TK hasn't made plenty of videos. Love Toby Keith but hate the rip-off record and DVD companies.
While I love Toby Keith and all these songs, I was looking for a CD of his music, not a DVD that doesn't work in my car etc. It would've been nice to know these are just music videos.
I have been looking for this DVD for a long time and I just got it and I'm looking forward to watching it. It was delivered fast Thanks!!!

Really and truly, just put it on and try not to sing along...that's right, you can't do it.

That puts him in a class by himself.

You can't go wrong if you are a Toby Keith fan.  I especially like "As good as I once was" and "I love this bar".  What a great country performer with a wonderful sense of humor.

I really appreciated how timely this product arrived. I had wanted it for my birthday but no one thought to get it for me. I ordered after the day and thought it would be weeks and it showed up in a matter of days. Well done!

This Toby Keith DVD is great, all the songs are brilliant, they are all music video's.

The songs on it are:

1. Should've Been A Cowboy

2. How Do You Like Me Now?!

3. Courtesy Of The Red, White And Blue
  (The Angry American)

4. Beer For My Horses

5. I Love This Bar

6. American Soldier

7. As Good As I Once Was

8. God Love Her

9. American Ride

10. Bullets In The Gun

All these songs are awesome and the video's are.
